<!doctype html>
<html lang="tr" data-i18n-title="page_title_archive"> <head>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/Fotograflar/altinbas-logo.svg" /> <meta charset="UTF-8" /> <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" /> <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/style.css" /> <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/style-dashboard.css" /> <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/lang-selector.css" /> <title>Belge Arşivi — Altınbaş Avukatlık Bürosu</title> </head> <body> <header class="navbar"> <div class="nav-left"> <a href="/lawyer/manage" class="brand-title"> <img src="/Fotograflar/altinbas-logo.svg" alt="Altınbaş Avukatlık Bürosu" style="height: 36px; filter: brightness(0) invert(1);" /> <span data-i18n="dash_back_panel">← Yönetime Dön</span> </a> </div> <div class="nav-right"> <div class="lang-selector"> <button type="button" class="lang-btn" id="langDropdownBtn" style="color: #FFFFFF; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);"> <span class="lang-flag" id="currentLangFlag">🇹🇷</span> <span class="lang-code" id="currentLangCode">TR</span> <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg> </button> <div class="lang-menu" id="langMenu"> <button type="button" onclick="setLanguage('tr')"><span>🇹🇷</span>Türkçe</button> <button type="button" onclick="setLanguage('en')"><span>🇬🇧</span>English</button> <button type="button" onclick="setLanguage('de')"><span>🇩🇪</span>Deutsch</button> <button type="button" onclick="setLanguage('fr')"><span>🇫🇷</span>Français</button> <button type="button" onclick="setLanguage('es')"><span>🇪🇸</span>Español</button> <button type="button" onclick="setLanguage('it')"><span>🇮🇹</span>Italiano</button> <button type="button" onclick="setLanguage('ru')"><span>🇷🇺</span>Русский</button> <button type="button" onclick="setLanguage('ar')"><span>🇸🇦</span>العربية</button> </div> </div> </div> </header> <main class="dashboard-container"> <section class="dashboard-section"> <h2 data-i18n="dash_archive">Kapanan / Silinen Dava Belge Arşivi</h2> <p class="empty-state" style="font-style: normal; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: left;" data-i18n="archive_desc">Kapatılan veya silinen dava dosyalarına ait belgeler güvenlik ve muhafaza amacıyla burada saklanır. İstediğiniz zaman erişebilir ve indirebilirsiniz. </p> <% if (archivedDocuments.length === 0) { %> <p class="empty-state" data-i18n="empty_archive">Arşivde kayıtlı herhangi bir belge bulunmuyor.</p> <% } else { %> <table class="cases-table"> <thead> <tr> <th data-i18n="doc_name">Belge Adı</th> <th data-i18n="dash_case_no">Eski Dosya No</th> <th data-i18n="dash_case_subject">Eski Dava Konusu</th> <th data-i18n="contact_email_lbl">Müvekkil E-posta</th> <th data-i18n="member_date">Arşive Alınma Tarihi</th> </tr> </thead> <tbody> <% archivedDocuments.forEach(function(document) { %> <tr> <td> <a href="/lawyer/documents/<%= document._id %>/download" target="_blank" style="color: var(--primary-dark); font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none;"> <%= document.FileName %> </a> </td> <td><strong><%= document.ArchivedCaseFileNumber || "—" %></strong></td> <td><%= document.ArchivedCaseSubject || "—" %></td> <td><%= document.ArchivedMemberEmail || "—" %></td> <td><span data-i18n-date="<%= document.ArchivedAt %>"><%= new Date(document.ArchivedAt).toLocaleDateString('tr-TR') %></span></td> </tr> <% }); %> </tbody> </table> <% } %> </section> </main> <script src="/JS/i18n.js"></script> </body>
</html>